      "comment": "CALLAHAN (5) made light work of a wide draw last time with a scorching early sectional and clocking 23.99 in a 1.3 lengths win at this track over 425m. Some good form is emerging from his last run. The hardest to beat again. ELECTRIC LOCH (3) could not have been more impressive last start in his a powerful 22.12 win at Shepparton over 390m. Should be in this for a long way. ASCEND IGLOO (1) finished well back at Shepparton last time when a 5.5 lengths sixth (22.68) but back to the course now of his latest success. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to his credit. Can measure up this time.",
